com.infinityrefactoring.reflections

Class ClassWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.infinityrefactoring.reflections.ClassWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the wrapped class

    public class ClassWrapper<T>
extends Object
    Wraps a java class for facilitate the handling of your members, using the Java Reflection API.
    Author:
    Thom√°s Sousa Silva (ThomasSousa96)
    See Also:
    wrap(Class), wrap(Object), Reflections, Predicates, PathExpression
